g-6190.gif\">旧字形</span></span>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>憐</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>暂无。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">pity<br>Basic explanation of words<br>pity<br>lián<br>See \"pity\".<br>pity<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［lián］<br>[\"Guangyun\" falls to Xianqie, level first, come. ]<br>Also known as \"Pity 2\".<br>(1) Pity; mercy.<br>(2) Love, love.<br>(3) Through \"neighbors\".<br>(4) Through \"stingy\". Stingy.<br>pity<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Mao Ji 1] [Heart Word Department] 　 Lian; Kangxi Strokes: 16; Page Number: Page 402 No. 12<br>〔古文〕㥕【Tang Yun】Luo Xian cut 【Ji Yun】【Rhyme Meeting】【Zheng Yun】Cut in the spiritual year,? Yinlian. 【Said Wen】Sorrow too. [Wu Yue Chunqiu Songs on the River] The same disease has pity for each other.　[Guangyun] Love also. [Lu Lianzi quotes ancient proverb] Sincere and pity, white hair.　[Jiyun] Li Zhenqie, sound neighbor. The same meaning. [Songs of Chu·Nine Debates] Travelling without friends, melancholy and self-pity. Ye Shangsheng.　The vulgar is pity.<br>pity<br>Source glyph<br>Character evolution: Xiaozhuan<br>Italics<br>Font comparison: Song Ti, Mainland China<br>Taiwan Minutes<br>Hong Kong Mingti<br>Japanese Ming Dynasty<br>Korean Ming Dynasty<br>Old glyph<br>pity<br>Name meaning<br>Nothing.</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">lián</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><span class=\"paragraph\">вм.</span> <span class=\"reference\">怜</span></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=憐\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=憐&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=憐\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=憐\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&nam